{"tid":2221861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[XGU愛國愛黨] 高度表揚校方保安","createTime":"2020-09-28T16:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T18:58:45.000Z","uid":269515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f053a3d052b45c8bfa251848adc4366dea862647","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFr69DrhDHO/?igshid=14v6hl6mbmm1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFr69DrhDHO%2F%3Figshid%3D14v6hl6mbmm1o&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=5a55a386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFr69DrhDHO%2F%3Figshid%3D14v6hl6mbmm1o&h=e56dcadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFr69DrhDHO/?igshid=14v6hl6mbmm1o</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n早幾日XGU俾班愛國愛黨人士拎住一堆工具入來拆牆叫囂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3333369526731720/?vh=e&amp;extid=Ilb999nU22JZfJgk&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F3333369526731720%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DIlb999nU22JZfJgk%26d%3Dn&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=6ea20640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3333369526731720/?vh=e&amp;extid=Ilb999nU22JZfJgk&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n校方就表示話「當大學增援保安到場時，他們陸續離開。」<br />\n<br />\n我就睇片睇到保安搭曬膊頭 舉曬手指公咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有一堆黑人BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要好好保護 唔怪得知要等咁耐增援啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我作為家長<br />\n好京d仔女係咁唔安全嘅大學讀書呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪可以闖入大學呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果果下學生被愛國人士襲擊 <br />\n唔知會唔會原告變被告呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知中國香港市人民第一大學點樣回應呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6974565e9f8a4c4a5431b0a2d4633fb495a9560","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"大大隻黑人BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6961657f8aecd4244fcb40651d5b9823ac91aec","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"大大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9895e8241078f041da8bb18f10e8756c6c007b7","tid":2221861,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"報左警未？"},{"pid":"5f711b797a67f21aca66039830d7ae43e0352a9f","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"依家話加閘wor<br />\n（但繼續唔查學生證）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1ddf07e1ad991224616698f4504b3040f8d4f9","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f711b797a67f21aca66039830d7ae43e0352a9f","tid":2221861,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"依家話加閘wor<br />\n（但繼續唔查學生證）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0